quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,17,"Alla yerﾉ擁nirii ﾉ兎e naafigeeﾉ兎 yeruuji ﾉ擁ﾉ擁: yeru jayngol, e yeru ndiyam, so tawii ko yerﾉ擁nde ﾉ兎 jayngol: ﾉ兎 nannde ko e oon kuﾉ橡砥ﾉ熔 jayngol ngam yaynaade, nde ngol jaawi o sikki ombo naftoro ooyre maggol kono tan ngol ﾃｱifi, ooyre nde majjiti, heddii tan ko nguleeki maggol, joom en keddii e niﾉ兎 e wemmbere hay huunde ﾉ兎 nji'ataa wonah feede e laawol."
  2,18,"Kamﾉ兎 ko fahﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 nanataa njaﾉ殿taa goonga, muumﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 kaalataa mo, wumﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 nji'ataa mbo, ﾉ兎 nduttotaako gaa majjere maﾉ橡兎."
  2,19,"So tawii ko yerﾉ擁nde ﾉ兎 e ndiyam: ﾉ兎 nanndi ko e toﾉ登 mawngo, e duule niﾉ橡砥ne e digaali e maje, ﾉ擁 jippii dow yimﾉ兎 ﾉ容ﾃｱﾆｴere mawnde heﾉ妬 ﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 ngoni e sukkude noppi maﾉ橡兎, sabu sattude kartaali ﾉ擁 e hulgol maayde, Alla na humpitii heeferﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n O ronkantaa ﾉ兎."
  2,20,"Jalbugol maje ﾉ容 na ﾉ容ﾉ殿 ﾉ熔ofde gite maﾉ橡兎, kala nde majal yaynii ﾉ兎 njawta, so ngal yaynaaki ﾉ兎 keddoo e niﾉ橡兎re, ﾉ兎 njahataa, so Alla welano itta nanﾉ容 e gite maﾉ橡兎 e kattanﾉ容 Makko kuﾉ鍍idinﾉ容, ﾉ兎 ngontaa heﾉ鍍ude ﾉ容, sabu ﾉ蓉urnaade ﾉ兎 goonga o. Kur'aan on waﾉ擁 toﾉ砥 ngo yeru, hito parﾃｱite wa'i no kaﾉ熔oje, ooyre maje ﾉ容 wa'i no googna peeﾃｱanatﾉ熔 ﾉ兎 seeﾉ預 kala, sukkude noppi ﾉ擁 wa'i no salaade ﾉ兎 goonga o, nanndal hakkunde naafigeeﾉ兎 e ﾉ兎e yerﾉ擁naaﾉ兎 ﾉ熔o woni waasde naftorde, yeru jayngol ngol: huﾉ橡砥ﾉ兎 ngol ﾉ兎e alaa ko naftorii heen sonaa niﾉ橡兎re e sumde, yeru ndiyam ﾉ預m: alaa ko ﾉ兎 naftori e toﾉ登 ngo sonaa kulol e ko digaali ﾉ擁 e maje ﾉ容 ﾉ妬ttini ﾉ兎, ko nii naafigeeﾉ兎 ngoniri, alaa ko ﾉ兎 nji'ata e Lislaam sonaa satteende."
  2,21,"Onon yimﾉ兎 ndewee joomi mon Kanko tan, wonaa hay gooto goﾉ遼熔, sabu ko Kanko tagi on O tagi leﾆｴﾆｴi gadiiﾉ擁 on, mbela joo ndaﾉ擁ron lette makko ﾉ熔ftaade jamirooje Makko ndeento-ﾉ熔n ﾉ擁 O haﾉ擁."
  2,22,"Ko Kanko waﾉ擁 leydi ndi wonani on mbertu ndaﾉ遼蓉di, O waﾉ擁 dow mon asamaan o mahaaﾉ熔 e ﾃｱeeﾃｱal, Kanko tigi neeminiri on jippinde toﾉ登 ngo, O fuﾉ溶i dow leydi ndi ﾉ妬ﾉ橡兎 leﾉ遼容 ceertuﾉ容, ﾉ容 ngoni njeﾉ蓉, taa mbaﾉ預nee Alla renndidiiﾉ兎 e nanndidiiﾉ兎 tawa oﾉ熔n nganndi alaa fof tagoowo sonaa Alla, teddungal e mawngu woodanii Mbo."
  2,23,"Onon yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎e so tawii oﾉ熔n cikkitii Kur'aan jippinaaﾉ熔 o dow jeyaaﾉ熔 Makko Muhammadu (jkw), Miﾉ容n cappoo on nde ngaddoton simoore wootere nanndunde heen, hay so wonii ko ﾉ砥rnde raﾉ橡砥de heen, noddee kala mbo njiﾉ遼熔n e wallidiiﾉ兎 mon, so tawii oﾉ熔n ngoonﾉ擁 e ko nodditorto-ﾉ熔n ko."
  2,24,"So tawii on mbaﾉ預ani ﾉ蓉um - te on mbaawantaa ﾉ蓉m pooma- ndeento-ﾉ容e jayngol kuﾉ橡妬rtengol yimﾉ兎 haanduﾉ兎 e lette, e nooneeji kaaﾆｴe e ko ﾉ兎 ndewannoo e goﾉ遼擁 kadi, ngol jayngol Alla tigi heblani ngol heeferﾉ兎 ﾉ兎."